<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">医学言葉その起こり</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>―“アダムのりんご”禁断の<ruby rubyText="み">実</ruby>は<ruby rubyText="じつ">実</ruby>は？</sentence>
